data.description: Stunning 5 bed 4 full bath home located in a well established neighborhood. As you enter you'll immediately notice the seamless flow of the open floorplan, inviting you to explore the abundance of space. Large formal living and dining, perfect for hosting gatherings. Spacious kitchen with ample counter space, island, walk in pantry, breakfast nook and breakfast bar. Family room featuring a WBF with gorgeous mantel, high ceilings and windows that fill the space with natural light. Office space with window seat, built in bookshelf and beautiful french doors. Master bedroom offers a cozy sitting area with bay windows that provides views to the outdoor pool. The en-suite bath offers a luxurious jetted tub, separate vanities, and a spacious walk in shower. Upstairs you will find an open game room, a media room with wet bar area, 4 large bedrooms with walk in closets and 2 full baths. Step outside into your own personal paradise, where the in-ground salt water pool awaits.
